(backported from commit db25c42c2e1f9c0d136420fff5e5700f7e771a6f)
[bot_kybele: This tree predates the
 xdp_update_skb_frags_info()/xdp_buff_get_skb_flags() rename, so kept the
 existing xdp_update_skb_shared_info()/xdp_buff_is_frag_pfmemalloc() call and
 only applied the upstream intent: changed the nr_frags arg from
 frag_page-head_page to new_nr_frags.]
Assisted-by: kybele:claude-opus-4.8
Signed-off-by: Cengiz Can <cengiz.can@canonical.com>
Acked-by: Hui Wang <hui.wang@canonical.com>
Acked-by: Jian Hui Lee <jianhui.lee@canonical.com>
